3.20	A_Generation	A Generation	A Generation (Polish: ) is a 1955 Polish film directed by Andrzej Wajda. It is based on the novel Pokolenie by Bohdan Czeszko, who also wrote the script, and it was Wajda's first film and the opening installment of what became his Three War Films trilogy set in the Second World War, completed by Kanal and Ashes and Diamonds.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/7/71/A_generation.jpg/220px-A_generation.jpg
